cu.explanation_en: Changing the CU's NGU IP address to 192.168.9.43 instead of 192.168.8.43 will cause unreachable subnet definitions, preventing proper NG-U interface communication.
cu.explanation_zh: 將 CU 的 NGU IP 地址從 192.168.8.43 更改為 192.168.9.43 會導致無法訪問的子網定義，阻止正確的 NG-U 接口通信。

du.explanation_en: Modifying the DL absolute frequency point A to 641008 instead of 640008 will cause frequency misalignment, leading to incorrect carrier frequency settings and potential synchronization issues.
du.explanation_zh: 將 DL 絕對頻率點 A 從 640008 修改為 641008 會導致頻率錯位，導致不正確的載波頻率設置和潛在的同步問題。
